'We've got one for you.
In fact, we've got two,

02:12.960 --> 02:16.840
'and that's ¤800.'

02:16.840 --> 02:19.960
Person with two S's...

02:19.960 --> 02:23.160
Siegfried Sassoon.

02:23.160 --> 02:24.320
No, that's four.

02:24.320 --> 02:27.840
'I'll buy a vowel.
I'd like an E, please.'

